= Left-Handed Mouse =
To get a left-handed mouse (i.e. to inverse left and right buttons) follow these instructions: <ref>
* Version 18: This solution is applicable to 18 with Wayland where input parameters are not yet all integrated in LXQt.
* Future versions: First try: ''Menu -> Preferences -> Keyboad and mouse''
</ref>
<br>

'''1.''' Create the required directory
{{CodeSelect|code=
mkdir --parents ~/.config/labwc
}} <br>

'''2.''' {{Open File|filename=
~/.config/labwc/rc.xml
}}

'''3.''' Type in or copy the following lines 

<ref> Source 
https://forums.kicksecure.com/t/how-to-get-a-left-hand-mouse-solved/1560
</ref>
{{CodeSelect|code=
<?xml version="1.0"?>
<labwc_config>
  <libinput>
    <device>
      <leftHanded>yes</leftHanded>
    </device>
  </libinput>
</labwc_config>
}}
